{"id": 2252, "genre": 1001, "title": "这么多年，哪些话题是你跟爸妈一直以来的沟通难点？", "description": "家长惯用伎俩——“大人说话小孩别插嘴”，但是不管你多大了，有些话依然难插嘴（图片来自：iStock）", "record_count": 2620, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180329155833TlaB9nkhCjUYbuRx.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-04-03T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 274176, "content": "跟老妈科普，永远不信我的，只信他人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166512}, {"id": 274177, "content": "我的爱好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225207}, {"id": 274178, "content": "根本不听你说的话 \n就一直怼你 \n说你做错了 不懂事之类的\n从小到大 \n从不当面夸奖\n总说什么 怕我骄傲\n事实上 我很自卑\n但家长并不是很在意\n有的时候 真的是非常的无语\n话到嘴边 听到说出的不能理解的话\n瞬间什么都不想说了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303705}, {"id": 274181, "content": "之前讨论过30岁以后再研究婚姻\n本来讨论的结果是可以不结婚了\n随自己的心意就好\n没过多久\n又说得结婚 \n说什么别人家的孩子26.27就结婚了\n你有什么不一样的啊\n无语 真的服气", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303705}, {"id": 274439, "content": "不是某些话题很难沟通！是我和他们基本没啥沟通?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054843}, {"id": 274185, "content": "他们认为结婚和生孩子是人生必需品", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051841}, {"id": 275211, "content": "不会沟通", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311299}, {"id": 274445, "content": "爸妈一直没有责怪我这些年的放浪与不成熟，我心里很内疚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1304928}, {"id": 274446, "content": "跟我妈聊过不婚不孕这个话题，她态度十分强硬，不允许我不结婚不生宝宝。后来跟一个不婚不孕的小姐姐聊过，发现首先需要经济独立，经济独立之后会有更多的话语权吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1304927}, {"id": 274447, "content": "考试成绩", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1304952}, {"id": 274449, "content": "“你说xxx学什么语言文学，这有什么用啊？！”\r\n“你们不要那么功利地去看待读书这件事，有些人学习就是兴趣使然啊，不是为了找工作的。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1304358}, {"id": 277266, "content": "学习学习，别人家的孩子，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275677}, {"id": 274452, "content": "在我们吵嘴皮子时，把我和我姐作比较，然后说还是我姐体贴有耐心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288287}, {"id": 278804, "content": "别人家的孩子永远是最好的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1281689}, {"id": 282132, "content": "不可以生气，不可以心情不好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346129}, {"id": 274454, "content": "由于父母二字，由于一些自己都不知道的深层次的意识，一些话，我们只能听着。所谓叛逆期，是冲动反驳与争吵不是吗？   ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289185}, {"id": 274458, "content": "和我妈不能讨论社会热点，都想说服对方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964934}, {"id": 274459, "content": "我是我，你是你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1083881}, {"id": 274716, "content": "我搞基。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275571}, {"id": 274208, "content": "嫁出去的女儿泼出去的水", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303879}, {"id": 274212, "content": "让妈不要再以孩子为中心，请她拥有自己的生活和世界，换来的是我怎么如此冷酷无情??‍♀️真心希望父母不要仅仅为了子女而活着", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303852}, {"id": 273971, "content": "健康相关话题，对于道听途说没有科学依据的事情深信不疑，并且不接受质疑", "image": null, "praise_count": 93, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194340}, {"id": 273972, "content": "在我感受到其实生活很难之后 我发现以前所有的沟通难点（我们各自的工作领域除外）都在于我自己的不懂事", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294836}, {"id": 273973, "content": "我好想和父母出柜，可我知道他们是无法理解的。现在又整天催我恋爱结婚，不知怎么办了", "image": null, "praise_count": 367, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1184394}, {"id": 273974, "content": "亲戚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720773}, {"id": 273975, "content": "从国企出来转行一开始没混好：早说了让你别走，现在这个样子，钱没存几个，好啦！", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284514}, {"id": 273976, "content": "我：?\r\n爸or妈：你咋哭了", "image": "img/option/option/20180403111353YbfLnphKIVsvqzP1.jpg", "praise_count": 139, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 751102}, {"id": 274489, "content": "性取向 婚姻观", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1304297}, {"id": 273978, "content": "永远不承认自己的错误", "image": null, "praise_count": 288, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 264156}, {"id": 273979, "content": "教老妈怎么用手机各种app 教一遍忘一遍 处于崩溃边缘????", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918581}, {"id": 273980, "content": "虽然我已经结婚并且备孕中，但是对于我妈认为的结婚为了生子生子为了养老的观念，我真的没有办法和她达成一致", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 543919}, {"id": 276284, "content": "是长辈说的 无论对错 都要听 不然就是对长辈的不尊重", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297241}, {"id": 273981, "content": "学习问题?还好爸妈很尊重我的意见", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014300}, {"id": 273982, "content": "我说我不太想生孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 162, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269862}, {"id": 275262, "content": "关于我在床头手机充电我会不会得癌，不喝温水会不会感冒的争论。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311897}, {"id": 273984, "content": "每次生病自己吃药吃不好都不肯去医院", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1302721}, {"id": 273985, "content": "当初让你学医你不学", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298587}, {"id": 273986, "content": "年紀到了就應該結婚生子～交通七大姑八大姨來說教", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1265441}, {"id": 273987, "content": "父亲出轨多年，发现多次从不解释就装作什么都没发生，母亲性情刚烈，一点小事不如意就开始反应激烈不依不饶，至于我懒的出奇，对未来毫无规划，亲戚们见了不好说什么对着我唉声叹气。\n可生活还是得继续啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1228489}, {"id": 273989, "content": "我妈说我不想生孩子以后谁愿意娶我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217481}, {"id": 274501, "content": "无法坐下来仔细听取并思考。越是至亲的人，如果无法沟通，越心冷。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659366}, {"id": 273990, "content": "现在找一个人恋爱好难\n不管是男人还是女人\n其实我感觉一个人的生活挺好的\n不想被父母一直催婚", "image": "img/option/option/20180403122047t683mnqcxEAo4Z7Y.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460983}, {"id": 273992, "content": "让他们理解哪怕只是包容生活方式、人生选择可以有很多种，不是只有他们认定的那一种，非常非常难。", "image": null, "praise_count": 89, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132422}, {"id": 273993, "content": "我真的是GAY", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 413092}, {"id": 273994, "content": "学习这事儿吧，不是足够努力就一定能学好的…就像他们工作也不是足够努力就能赚大钱的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1281633}, {"id": 273995, "content": "“我是过来人，我懂得比你多。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1300413}, {"id": 273996, "content": "这里是LGBT社区？", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 866618}, {"id": 273997, "content": "我：我找了个女朋友\n妈：存多少钱了？啥时候结婚？\n我：？？？我才谈一个月", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287004}, {"id": 273998, "content": "花钱出去玩和学习之间", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299260}, {"id": 273999, "content": "他们觉得人生一定要有孩子，不生孩子的人都是生不出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1302804}]}